{"tid":629673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫生：醉酒休息切忌平躺","createTime":"2018-04-15T01:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T03:43:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc745977fa84b59b848b061248637ed19423af78","tid":629673,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:57:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180415/20362014?_ga=2.45845412.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20362014%3F_ga%3D2.45845412.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=3JZvmOjVobjbrusMEVzyybIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=31a8b2cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20362014%3F_ga%3D2.45845412.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=ac679db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180415/20362014?_ga=2.45845412.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n醫生：醉酒休息切忌平躺<br />\n<br />\n3.7K<br />\n要聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/wine.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2Fwine.jpg&h=08f08a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醉酒令肌肉協調不順，加上意識不清，易將吐出的嘔吐物重新吸入，導致窒息噎死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n家庭醫生關嘉美向《蘋果》表示，飲酒嘔吐致噎死的情況時有發生。她解釋指，醉酒令肌肉協調不順，加上個人意識不清，很容易將吐出的嘔吐物重新吸入體內，導致窒息噎死。她建議若照顧醉酒者，切忌讓他們平躺，最好打側休息，令嘔吐物更易吐出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關嘉美指出，正常一般人嘔吐，在意識清楚下會將嘔吐物向前吐出體外，但在醉酒的情況下卻未必做到。她解釋指，醉酒後肌肉協調不順，個人意識模糊，很容易將本來向前吐出的嘔吐物重新吸入體內，所以嘔吐物容易堵塞呼吸道，窒息噎死，屬於常見的飲酒致死情況。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，醉酒沒有自救能力，吃得越飽，醉酒會有更多嘔吐物，情況就越危險，故不建議獨自一人喝至大醉，最好有人陪伴照顧。她建議照顧者切忌將醉者平躺，否則容易重新吸入嘔吐物，應以打側休息為佳，令嘔吐物容易吐出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\nL&rsquo;OR&Eacute;AL前總監　疑宿醉嘔吐噎死移居台30年　伏屍台北寓所<br />\n<br />\n要聞 3小時前"},{"pid":"cacef6cfc37776746e80f393009b5ecc426be24d","tid":629673,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}